# Regenerable experiment scratch never gets committed (AGENTS.md rule 5: bulky or churning
# data goes to the Notion experiments area with a SHA-256 manifest, not git). Patterns cover
# every study dir under research/: TraceScalingAblation._report_sink writes *_seed<N>.json,
# every runner writes .usage.json next to its --out, inspection dumps are per-step
# prediction/critique blobs, and figs/ pngs are rendered from the tracked SVG sources.
**/*_seed*.json
**/*.usage.json
**/*.inspection.json
**/*.log
**/figs/*.png

# The contamination probe's sole surviving raw evidence (the zero-shot table in
# docs/research/world_model_findings.md layer 1; methodology in
# ../reference/rag-scaling-methodology.md).
!rag_opt_results/contam.log
